Rules.InvariantScript: "Please review your desk reservation details and press Confirm to proceed with your reservation"

ForAll(
    selectedDesks,
    Patch(
        List_DeskReservations,
        Defaults(List_DeskReservations),
        {
            Title: selectedPerson.DisplayName & " " & ThisRecord.Title,
            DeskText: ThisRecord.Title,
            //CheckOutFrom_DateTime: DateAdd(startTime, /*TimeZoneOffset(),*/ TimeUnit.Minutes ), 
            CheckOutFrom_DateTime: DateAdd(startTime, DateDiff(startTime, endTime,TimeUnit.Minutes), TimeUnit.Minutes ),
            CheckOutFrom_Text: startTime,
            CheckOutFrom_Number:Value(Text(startTime,"yyyymmddhmm")),
            //CheckOutTo_DateTime: DateAdd(endTime, /*TimeZoneOffset(),*/ TimeUnit.Minutes ),
            CheckOutTo_DateTime: DateAdd(endTime, DateDiff(startTime, endTime, TimeUnit.Minutes), TimeUnit.Minutes ),
            CheckOutTo_Text: endTime,
            CheckOutTo_Number: Value(Text(endTime,"yyyymmddhmm")),
            ReservedBy_Person: {
                '@odata.type': "#Microsoft.Azure.Connectors.SharePoint.SPListExpandedUser",
                Claims: "i:0#.f|membership|" &  selectedPerson.Mail,
                Department: "",
                DisplayName: selectedPerson.DisplayName,
                Email: selectedPerson.Mail,
                JobTitle: "",
                Picture: ""
            }
        }
    )
);
Concurrent(
    Reset(ddTimeTo),
    Reset(ddTimeFrom),
    Reset(Calendar_1),
    Clear(selectedDesks),
    Set(
        selectedDate,
        Blank()
    ),
    Set(
        startTime,
        Today()
    ),
    Set(
        endTime,
        Today()
    )
);

Navigate(Success)
